column2: SELECT TOP # p.oiii_#_reqw_err as oir_e, p.h_beta_reqw_err as hbr_e, p.nii_#_reqw_err as nir_e, p.h_alpha_reqw_err as har_e, oiii_#_reqw as oir, h_beta_reqw as hbr, nii_#_reqw as nir, h_alpha_reqw as har, p.specObjID, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger         FROM galSpecLine as p    JOIN ZooSpec AS zs ON p.specObjID = zs.specobjid    WHERE p.clean=# and zs.nvote >= # and zs.p_cw > #
